reat wines with excellent acidity, soft tannins and abundant, intense aromas of black plum and jammy blackberry. These wines are often elegant and well balanced.</span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ bOeEnL pf-199_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-avest iZvAhG pf-200_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-202_">ALVARINHO</span></h3><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-203_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-205_">The finest white grape in Vinho Verde, exhibiting floral qualities and sweet citrus notes balanced with acidity and minerality.</span></p></div></div></div><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-206_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-208_">Interested in learning more about our grape varietals?<br>Why not come and try our Wine Blending Workshop!</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-8896" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bSqaIl hxsZTX pf-209_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-hkgtus clVJp"><div class="sc-bBHHxi gGMCwe pf-210_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-JkixQ bOeEnL pf-211_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-avest iZvAhG pf-212_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-214_">SUBSCRIBE TO OUR MAILING LIST</span></h3><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-215_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-217_">*INDICATES REQUIRED</span></p><form target="_blank" action="" method="POST" data-pf-type="MailChimp" class="sc-iWBNLc jVlzqx pf-218_"><input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" name="FNAME" required=""/><input type="text" placeholder="Email Address*" name="EMAIL" required=""/><button><span>Subscribe</span></button></form></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-d91d" data-pf-type="Section" cla